image_analysis.description: A photograph of a small bathroom or powder room. The room features a white toilet, a white pedestal sink, and a black-framed mirror. On top of the toilet tank are several cleaning supplies (bottles) and a roll of toilet paper. A white towel hangs on a rack to the left. The floor is tiled with small white square tiles. A small glass shelf with toiletries is mounted next to the sink. A light fixture is visible above the mirror.
image_analysis.layout: Interior shot of a bathroom, angled from the doorway.
